// QuestionRenderer
// Renders a Claude question using the AI-UI component system.
// Tries to parse the question text as a JSON UIComponent tree; falls back to a
// Card wrapping a Markdown component; falls back further to SimpleTextQuestion
// if the component type is not registered.

FUNCTION SimpleTextQuestion(text, isLoading, onSubmit) -> JSX
  Renders a textarea for free-text response and a Submit button.
  Submit disabled while isLoading or response is empty.
  Calls onSubmit when submitted.

---

FUNCTION QuestionRenderer(question, onAction, isLoading) -> JSX        EXPORT
  CALLS: AIUIRenderer (renderer), validateComponent (registry)
  1. Builds uiComponent: IF question.text starts with "{", attempts JSON.parse.
     On failure or non-JSON text, wraps text in a Card > Markdown component tree.
  2. Validates uiComponent.type via validateComponent. IF invalid, renders
     SimpleTextQuestion with handleAction('submit', text) as the submit callback.
  3. Otherwise renders AIUIRenderer with uiComponent, handleAction, and
     disabled:isLoading injected into componentProps.
  Dims the rendered UI (opacity 0.6) while isLoading.

---

FUNCTION handleAction(actionId, payload) -> void
  Skips if isLoading. Otherwise calls onAction(actionId, payload).
